# 2. IDENTIDADE

**Mission Control**  um dashboard open-source de orquestrao de agentes IA, desenvolvido pela Builderz Labs. Fornece uma interface nica para gerenciamento de frotas de agentes, despacho de tarefas, rastreamento de custos e coordenao de workflows multi-agente  auto-hospedado, zero dependncias externas, powered by SQLite.

- **Repositrio**: https://github.com/builderz-labs/mission-control
- **Licena**: MIT (open-source, self-hosted)
- **Stack tecnolgica**:
  - **Frontend**: Next.js 16 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript 5.7, Tailwind CSS 3.4
  - **Backend**: Next.js API routes, SQLite (better-sqlite3, WAL mode), Zustand state management
  - **UI/UX**: Recharts (grficos), React Flow (fluxos), XTerm (terminal)
  - **Autenticao**: scrypt hashing, session tokens, RBAC (viewer/operator/admin), Google Sign-In opcional
  - **Real-time**: WebSocket + Server-Sent Events (SSE) com smart polling
  - **Testes**: Vitest (282 unitrios) + Playwright (295 E2E)
- **Porta padro**: `:3000` (dashboard), `:18789` (gateway OpenClaw)
- **Verso atual**: 2.0.1 (20260414)
- **Releases**: Tags semnticas no GitHub; imagens Docker multiarch publicadas no GHCR (`ghcr.io/builderz-labs/mission-control:latest`)

